---
title: "isValidSignature - ERC-1271 (Payment Abstraction V2)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_decode: isValidSignature(orderHash, encodedOrder) called by CowSwap Settlement
    q_decode --> q_check_auction: decode GPv2Order from encodedOrder
    q_check_auction --> q_check_amount: live auction exists for sellToken
    q_check_auction --> q_revert_no_auction: no live auction
    q_revert_no_auction --> [*]: revert NoActiveAuction
    q_check_amount --> q_check_buy_token: sellAmount > 0
    q_check_amount --> q_revert_amount: sellAmount == 0
    q_revert_amount --> [*]: revert InvalidAmount
    q_check_buy_token --> q_check_receiver: buyToken == s_assetOut
    q_check_buy_token --> q_revert_token: buyToken mismatch
    q_revert_token --> [*]: revert InvalidBuyToken
    q_check_receiver --> q_check_min_bid: receiver == address(this)
    q_check_receiver --> q_revert_receiver: invalid receiver
    q_revert_receiver --> [*]: revert InvalidReceiver
    q_check_min_bid --> q_calc_expected: sellAmount USD value >= minBidUsdValue
    q_check_min_bid --> q_revert_min: below minimum bid
    q_revert_min --> [*]: revert BelowMinBidValue
    q_calc_expected --> q_check_buy_amount: expectedBuyAmount = getAssetOutAmount(sellAmount, sellToken, buyToken, elapsed)
    q_check_buy_amount --> q_check_partial: buyAmount >= expectedBuyAmount
    q_check_buy_amount --> q_revert_price: buyAmount < expectedBuyAmount
    q_revert_price --> [*]: revert InsufficientBuyAmount
    q_check_partial --> q_check_kind: order is partiallyFillable
    q_check_partial --> q_revert_fill: not partially fillable
    q_revert_fill --> [*]: revert MustBePartiallyFillable
    q_check_kind --> q_return_valid: orderKind == sell
    q_check_kind --> q_revert_kind: invalid order kind
    q_revert_kind --> [*]: revert InvalidOrderKind
    q_return_valid --> [*]: return ERC1271_MAGIC_VALUE

    note right of q_calc_expected
        INV-001: buyAmount must meet or exceed the auction curve price at current elapsed time
        INV-002: Orders must be partially fillable to allow gradual auction clearing
        INV-003: Receiver must be the auction contract itself to collect proceeds
        INV-004: Minimum bid USD value prevents dust bids
    end note
